<br />Was it only BIOS that couldn't reprogram the palette in EGA modes, or did the card's hardware restrict the color palette whenever the dot clock was set below the frequency for 640x350? I seem to remember that a CGA would just use EGA green intensity for all three channels' intensity.

		

